&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt; Stage-Gate &amp;amp; Process Compliance Support&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support the operation and monitoring of &lt;strong&gt;Stage-Gate processes&lt;/strong&gt; across projects&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track and verify whether required deliverables, assumptions, and approvals are properly completed at each stage&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support validation of &lt;strong&gt;RACI alignment&lt;/strong&gt; across cross-functional teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify gaps, misalignments, or process deviations and escalate appropriately&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt; Independent Cross-Check &amp;amp; Validation&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform &lt;strong&gt;independent cross-checks&lt;/strong&gt; on key project inputs, including:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cost estimates and major CapEx assumptions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Project schedules and milestone logic&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Long Lead Items (LLI) procurement plans&lt;/li&gt;
