&lt;p&gt;The Senior Manager, Project Finance will play a vital role within the Hanwha Renewables organization to enable our vision of becoming the leading solar solution provider in the Americas. The Senior Manager of Project Finance is expected to draw upon an extensive finance background and direct experience to lead the successful finance utility-scale ground mount PV power plants and BESS projects. As a senior member of the organization, the Senior Manager of Project Finance will work independently to develop, finance, and conduct project sell-down transactions.&lt;/p&gt;
